No! Kwaviya viyaviya ivo viyaviya, Mulungu kodahaze kuulanga isi yose?
Munhu yoyose kodaha kulonga, "Vino uvwizi wangu wolagusa ukweli wa Mulungu na kumwing'ha utunhizo wake, habali niye nolagusa kuwa ni munhu wa uhasanyi?"
